- Build from shadcn/ui primitives; keep components minimal and composable.
- Variants: use `class-variance-authority` (CVA). Export `{Component, componentVariants}` from the same file.
- Class names: merge with `cn()`; never concatenate manually.
- Accessibility: preserve focus styles, aria props, keyboard interactions from Radix primitives.
- Composition: prefer Slot API (`@radix-ui/react-slot`) for polymorphism via `asChild`.
- Files: one component per file; colocate stories/examples elsewhere if needed.
- Theming: respect Tailwind CSS variables; dark mode ready.
- Do not inline custom styles; add Tailwind utilities or extend variants.

